goals.question: What is the distribution of wind speed for each wind direction category?

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['speed'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['speed'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['speed'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Wind Speed (m/s)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speed?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()

    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.scatter(data['dir'], data['speed'], alpha=0.5)
    plt.xlabel('Wind Direction (degrees)')
    plt.ylabel('Wind Speed (m/s)')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between wind speed and wind direction?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))
    heatmap, xedges, yedges = np.histogram2d(data['latitude'], data['longitude'], bins=50, weights=data['speed'])
    extent = [yedges[0], yedges[-1], xedges[0], xedges[-1]]
    plt.imshow(heatmap.T, extent=extent, origin='lower', cmap='coolwarm')
    plt.colorbar(label='Wind Speed (m/s)')
    plt.xlabel('Longitude')
    plt.ylabel('Latitude')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind vectors across the latitude and longitude coordinates?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    boxplot = data.boxplot(column='speed', by='dirCat', ax=ax)
    ax.set_xlabel('Wind Direction Category')
    ax.set_ylabel('Wind Speed (m/s)')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of wind speed for each wind direction category?')
    ax.axhline(y=data['speed'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
